overview: When Xander agreed to partiticipate in a paid memory test with his wife, he had no idea he'd wind up being locked away in an observation room with Nicolette, a smoking hot assistant whose only job is to discipline Xander when he gets and answer wrong. Lucky for Xander, Nicolette's idea of punishment is anyhing but unpleasant.
title: Nympho Nurses & Dirty Doctors 3
